DO NOT Forget About Hell is Us - NEW GAMEPLAY
In this video, I'm going to be talking a little bit more about Hell is Us. This is a game you've seen several times on our channel already. I covered this back in May when I went to Rogue Factor Studio in Montreal to play the game there. We did a preview on it, then saw it again at Gamescom just last week, and spent some time talking to the developers while I was there as well.
